---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../config/site";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero 区域 -->
    <div class="bg-orange-50">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          [Last Revised: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}]
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 内容区域 -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            This Privacy Policy explains how {siteConfig.url} collects, uses, shares, and protects information when you visit {siteConfig.url}. By using the Site, you agree to this Policy. If you do not agree, please stop using the Site.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Scope</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            This Policy applies to our Site and related pages/emails. It does not apply to third-party sites or services we do not control.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Personal Information (PII): Name, email, and message contents when you contact us, subscribe, or submit comments/feedback.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Non-PII/Usage Data: IP address, device/browser type, language, pages viewed, time on page, referrer, coarse location.</p>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Cookies/Similar Tech: For Site operation, analytics, preference storage, and (where applicable) affiliate attribution.</p>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Reviews/Content: Comments or reviews you submit may be displayed and republished per our Terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. How We Use Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            To operate and improve the Site, respond to inquiries, send requested content, conduct analytics and security, comply with law, and enforce our Terms. You can unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We may share information with service providers/contractors (hosting, analytics, email, attribution), disclose information for legal reasons or rights/safety protection, and transfer data in a business transaction. We do not sell your personal information for money. Some analytics/ads disclosures may be deemed a "sale/share" under certain state laws — see Rights and Choices.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Cookies and Tracking Choices</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            You can block/delete cookies in your browser (some features may not work). If your browser sends Global Privacy Control (GPC), we treat it as an opt-out of "sale/share" where required by law. We do not respond to legacy Do Not Track (DNT) signals.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Affiliate Links and Third-Party Sites</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Articles may include affiliate links; if you purchase via a link, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. We clearly disclose affiliate relationships and they do not influence our conclusions. Third-party sites follow their own policies — please review them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Retention and Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We retain information as needed for the purposes in this Policy and apply reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards. No method is 100% secure — please take care online.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">8. 8.International Transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We may process/store information in the United States and other countries with different data protection rules. We take steps required by law to protect data during transfers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">9. Children</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The Site is for a general audience and is not directed to children under 13 (or the minimum age in your region). If you believe a child provided personal information, contact us to delete it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">10. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Emails: Unsubscribe via links in our emails.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
Cookies: See Section 5 for browser/GPC controls.</p>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
EEA/UK (GDPR/UK-GDPR): You may request access, rectification, deletion, restriction, portability, object to processing, and withdraw consent (without affecting prior lawful processing).</p>
<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
California (CCPA/CPRA): You may request to know, access, delete, correct, and opt out of "sale/share" of personal information, without discrimination. To submit a request or opt out, contact us and include "CCPA/CPRA Request." We may verify your request (for example, email confirmation). We do not knowingly sell/share personal information of users under 16.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">11. Law Enforcement and Legal</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We may disclose information when required by law, court order, or to protect our rights, users, or the public.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We may update this Policy from time to time and will revise the Effective Date. Material changes may include additional notice. Please review periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">13. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Questions or requests about this Policy or our data practices:
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Email: <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>{siteConfig.email}</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 